videos.description: Dillon Brooks misses the first shot, but is able to fight his way through bodies to get the tipped ball and is able to finagle a tough and-1 basket for the Grizzlies through contact.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Brooks won't give up on this play!) 2021/05/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brooks won't give up on this play!

videos.description: Desmond Bane talks a fair amount of trash to Georges Niang after he buries a buzzer-beating 3-pointer in Niang's grill to end the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bane talks trash to Niang after draining buzzer-beating 3) 2021/05/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bane talks trash to Niang after draining buzzer-beating 3

videos.description: Ja Morant uses a behind-the-back move to shake Mike Conley, then speeds to the basket to finesse in a silky smooth finger roll.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Morant mixes up Conley for silky bucket) 2021/05/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Morant mixes up Conley for silky bucket

videos.description: Rudy Gobert fouled out of the game, but that didn't stop him falling dramatically to the ground after taking a small push from Kyle Anderson.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Gobert pulls out tremendous flop despite being fouled out) 2021/05/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gobert pulls out tremendous flop despite being fouled out

videos.description: Dillon Brooks gives the Grizzlies a 112-109 lead as he takes the inbound pass and slips around the defense to score an easy clutch layup.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Dillon Brooks scores clutch basket late as 8-seed Grizzlies take Game 1) 2021/05/23 ESHEET
